reviews.reviewText: This set of knives is just ok. They do what they are supposed to do, no big wow factor. Matter of fact one of the knives started to look like it was rusting, just a couple weeks after we bought the set. The other knives still look OK though. Would probably not buy again.

reviews.reviewText: This knife set is a great price, they look great, and are sharp, unfortunately they are very poor quality, and rust easily. IMO they are not worth it.
